 AI 颠覆间撕裂，正通过“全球混血”模式突围；韩日则通过政府组团模式，分别在全屋智能生态和务实社会应用领域发力。整体呈现出 AI 从“对话服务”向“物理交互”与“全局记忆”进化的核心趋势。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_0d2d4723.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"阿里研究院","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":56,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_41fe0f75","title":"2026-02-03 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-03-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-03 08:52:14","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_41fe0f75.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":68,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_fc8fb3b8","title":"喝点 VC｜a16z 应用团队：在如今软件可被快速构建的时代，护城河的重要性反而比以往任何时候都更高","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==&mid=2247513862&idx=1&sn=9a61f2ba2b4fcae7fc16eeef7986a406","date":"2026-02-03 02:54:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_fc8fb3b8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Z Potentials","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":118,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_a9b9791f","title":"AI 干掉 80% App 实录：他用 OpenClaw 40 分钟完成自动修 bug、控制智能家居、通宵监控陌生人","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247625162&idx=2&sn=7a5d0f2560b51b067a8c003eff544b49","date":"2026-02-03 02:18:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_a9b9791f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"硅星人Pro","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_2a5415de","title":"⚡ 揭秘 GitHub 的 AI 革命：Jared Palmer 揭晓 Agent HQ 与编程智能体的未来","link":"https://www.latent.space/p/inside-githubs-ai-revolution-jared","date":"2026-02-02 15:30:27","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_2a5415de.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Latent Space","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":2,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_c3f36434","title":"AI 社交元年：Moltbook 背后的机机交互革命与行业新机遇","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&mid=2650677128&idx=2&sn=ee75de9c09136a0b6c9f0a708c289a5f","date":"2